hat ignore overdispersion or only\nconsider the proportions. We demonstrate the power of our method in an analysis\nof a data set evaluating the effects of nutrient intake on human gut microbiome\ncomposition. Our results have clearly shown that the nutrient intake is\nstrongly associated with the human gut microbiome.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 May 2013 09:20:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-24"}
